PersonalMission.Name: SPG-15: War Gods
PersonalMission.Description: An SPG that survives for as long as possible is a real asset for the team. Keep firing one shell after another while trying not to get caught under enemy fire. Take your time and think twice before \"pulling the trigger\", since \"one shotone hit\" is the best strategy for a vehicle with a long reload time.

Primary.Conditions:
Be among the top 5 players on your team by experience earned
  Enable your allies to cause 1,000 HP of damage to enemy vehicles by stunning or immobilizing them
